│                                                                                            │
│ ### 3. Root Cause Analysis                                                                 │
│                                                                                            │
│ The root cause is in a helper function used by many `visit` methods in InstCombine,        │
│ specifically `InstCombinerImpl::visitOperand()`. This function is designed to recursively  │
│ simplify operands of an instruction. If an operand is simplified, the original operand     │
